```plantuml
@startuml michaelsrichter_azure.owasp

actor Developer
participant "ASP.NET MVC App" as ASP
participant "Node.js App" as Node
participant "ModSecurity" as ModSec
participant "OWIN Middleware" as OWIN
participant "Azure AD" as AzureAD
participant "Azure ARM" as ARM

Developer -> ASP: Deploy using ARM Template
ASP -> ARM: Deploy Resources

Developer -> ASP: Access Secure App
ASP -> OWIN: Authenticate Request
OWIN -> AzureAD: Validate Token
AzureAD -> OWIN: Return Token
OWIN -> ASP: Grant Access

Developer -> Node: Access Node.js App
Node -> ModSec: Inspect Request
ModSec -> Node: Forward Request (if safe)

ModSec -> Node: Block Request (if malicious)

Node -> Developer: Return Response

Developer -> ASP: Test Insecure App
ASP -> ModSec: Inspect Request
ModSec -> ASP: Block Request (if malicious)

ModSec -> ASP: Allow Request (if safe)
ASP -> Developer: Return Response

@enduml
```